"      Oxybutynin: Drug information",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"drug drug_pediatric\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?39/11/40117?source=related_link\">",
"      Oxybutynin: Pediatric drug information",
